**Horrifying Wolf** | Werewolf Miscellaneous  
__Basics__
Whoever perceives the Horrifying Wolf, may not investigate again in the following night. 
__Details__
Whenever another player investigates the Horrifying Wolf at night, the are obstructed and may not investigate again in the following night.
This applies even if the investigation does not directly see the Horrifying Wolfs role - either due to a non-role type investigation or a disguise applied on the Horrifying Wolf. 

__Simplified__
Whoever perceives the Horrifying Wolf, may not investigate again in the following night. 

__Formalized__
Inherit: `Pack Lycan`

__Card__
The Horrifying Wolf is veri spooki.
